title: Шестое чувство
overview: The documentary series explores human supernatural abilities. In each episode of the program, famous actor Vadim Demchog talks about the most incredible and mind-blowing possibilities, such as telepathy, clairvoyance, the ability to control the weather, attract wealth and much more. What is this - a gift of nature or the result of long and persistent training of consciousness? Answers to these and many other questions in the "Sixth Sense" project. The program involves experts, as well as people with phenomenal abilities.
